## DESIGN CONSTRAINTS (apply to all components above)

- Background: gnBgDeepest (#09090F) on all screens
- Cards: gnBgSurface (#12121C), 10-12dp corners, gnBorderCard 1dp stroke, elevation=0
- Fonts: GameNativeFontFamily (Outfit) via PluviaTypography everywhere
- Do NOT define new colors — only existing gn_* tokens from Color.kt
- No elevation shadows — stroke borders only
- Presence state colors:
    ONLINE  → gnNeonTeal
    IN_GAME → gnAccentPrimary
    AWAY    → gnNeonOrange
    OFFLINE → gnTextTertiary
- In-game panel: gnBgDeepest.copy(alpha=0.95f) so game is faintly visible behind
- Message bubbles: sent=gnAccentPrimary bg white text, received=gnBgElevated gnTextPrimary
- Invite banner: always uses gnAccentPrimary border tint so it stands out from regular cards
- All LazyColumn/LazyRow keys must be stable: key = { it.appId }, key = { it.id }, etc.
- All network calls on Dispatchers.IO, all UI state updates on Dispatchers.Main
- All loading states show shimmer — never show "Loading..." plain text
- imePadding() on the chat input row so keyboard never covers the text field
- The in-game chat panel MUST NOT pause or affect the running game process in any way
- The edge handle must always be visible during gameplay so users can always access chat
